0:39:20.680,0:39:24.320
Svondo ye musi we Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:39:24.320,0:39:27.060
Tumira shoko iri kune vatungamiri vako.

0:39:27.060,0:39:32.940
Kana iwe uine mukana wekuita musangano nevatungamiriri vako, ndapota uvaudze,

0:39:32.940,0:39:46.860
"Kuchengeta chigumbu kunofanana nekupara mhosva nokuti kusakanganwira kunotipinza muhusungwa.

0:39:46.860,0:39:49.020
Kunotiisa mujeri, mukeji. "

0:39:49.020,0:39:55.920
Iwe unongowana kuti kune muganhu pane zvaunogona kuita.

0:39:55.920,0:39:57.700
Ndinokwanisa kuita izvi - asi  pane muganhu.

0:39:57.700,0:40:00.640
Zvinotiisa mujeri.

0:40:00.640,0:40:04.780
Uye izvo zvisina kuitwa zvakanaka hazviina kuitwa zvachose.

0:40:04.780,0:40:10.440
Kusakanganwira kune ngozi kune ramangwana rako.

0:40:10.440,0:40:14.080
Usanyepera kukanganwira; usanyepera kuda.

0:40:14.080,0:40:20.560
Sezvandareva, nzira yaunoda nayo ndiyo nzira yauchadiwa nayo.

0:40:20.560,0:40:24.520
Nzira yaunokanganwira ndiyo nzira yaunokanganwirwa.

0:40:24.520,0:40:27.160
Chero chipi zvacho chaunoda kuita, rega chibve mumwoyo wako.

0:40:27.160,0:40:30.900
Mwari ndiye mupi we mubayiro.

0:40:30.900,0:40:37.880
Kana iwe uchiramba uchipa vamwe mhosva,hauzo tendeuka

0:40:37.880,0:40:46.000
"A hongu, anovirima zvikuru kwandiri" - hauzo tendeuka.

0:40:46.000,0:40:50.300
Bvuma zvinhu zvose, "Hungu, izvi hazvina kunaka. Zvakanaka. Ndinoziva kuti ndini wacho."

0:40:50.300,0:40:58.680
Nokuti hatisi kurwisa nyama neropa; Kupomera vamwe iwe hauzo tendeuka.

0:40:58.680,0:41:03.600
Mwari anowanzoshandisa chero chinhu.

0:41:03.600,0:41:09.800
Iwe unogona kunge wakagara, mumwe munhu ouya ozotanga kukurova.

0:41:09.800,0:41:12.040
"A, ko chii chandaita?"

0:41:12.040,0:41:15.520
Yeuka iwe uri mu Kristu - zviri nani kuti umhanye, ibva pa nzvimbo yacho.

0:41:15.520,0:41:20.280
Usatsiva nokuti hauzivi chikonzero nei izvi zvaitika.

0:41:20.280,0:41:25.740
Zvose, "Sei Mwari?" ...

0:41:25.740,0:41:30.660
Mwari anowanzoshandisa chero chinhu - funga nezvazvo.

0:41:30.660,0:41:33.880
Chero chinhu chii?

0:41:33.880,0:41:40.760
Zvinhu zvakawanda zvakashandiswa munguva yakapfuura kukugadzirira asi iwe wakakundikana.

0:41:40.760,0:41:43.300
Ndinogona kukupa mienzaniso yakanaka.

0:41:43.300,0:41:48.980
Chinzvimbo chevamwe venyu chakatorwa ne "moto".

0:41:48.980,0:41:57.640
Iwe wakanga uri pachigaro, uye muteedzeri wako akasimudzirwa kuva pamusoro pako, mukuru wako.

0:41:57.640,0:42:05.240
Iwe zvino unoti, "Ee?" Ndinoshumira Mwari, ndinotsanya ne kunyengetera. Ini ndinogara ndiri muchechi.

0:42:05.240,0:42:16.280
wandairayiridza, anogona kukwidziridzwa kuva mukuru wangu? Oo kwete; nomoto. "

0:42:16.280,0:42:18.300
Iwe unomhanyira ku n'anga.

0:42:18.300,0:42:25.780
Iwe unoti, "Uyu ndiye ari pasi pangu - iye akakurudzirwa ndiye ave mukuru wangu ikozvino. Ndiye avekundipa mirayiridzo."

0:42:25.780,0:42:28.540
N'anga ichati, "Unoda kuti ndiitei?"

0:42:28.540,0:42:31.760
"Nemoto, nemoto."

0:42:31.760,0:42:33.660
Iwe unopiwa upfu.

0:42:33.660,0:42:38.720
Sezvo iye zvino ava mukuru wako, iwe unofanirwa kupukuta tafura yake - iwe unodonhedzera upfu ipapo.

0:42:38.720,0:42:43.620
Ndiwo magumo. Mukuru anorwara oendeswa kose kose

0:42:43.620,0:42:50.240
Mwedzi umwe, mwedzi miviri - iwe unotora chinzvimbo chacho.

0:42:50.240,0:42:56.660
Iwe hauzivi kuti ...

0:42:56.660,0:43:04.760
Tarisai, kukurumidza kuti murume wacho akakomborerwa.

0:43:04.760,0:43:09.120
Muvambi haasi iye muridzi asi mupedzisi.

0:43:09.120,0:43:15.620
Svondo ye musi we Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:43:15.620,0:43:17.480
Izvi ndizvo zvidzidzo zvatinofanira kudzidza.

0:43:17.480,0:43:28.580
Magamba akawanda akaparara; varume vakuru kuru, vapfumi, vakafanira ...

0:43:28.580,0:43:32.160
nekuda kwekuti muvambi haasi iye muridzi asi mupedzisi.

0:43:32.160,0:43:43.520
Kana ukasapedzisa zvakanaka, zvose zvawakararamira zvaenda uye nhoroondo pamusoro pako yadzimwa.

0:43:43.520,0:43:50.240
Zvakaipa izvo vanhu vanoita zvinorama vasisipo

0:43:50.240,0:43:58.620
Vazhinji venyu makagadzirirwa kune zera risati razvarwa, seva apositori -

0:43:58.620,0:44:04.460
ivo vakagadzirirwa kune zera raive risati razvarwa, kuitira kuti kana vafa,

0:44:04.460,0:44:08.680
basa ravo raizorarama kune zera risati razvarwa.

0:44:08.680,0:44:12.540
Izvi ndizvo zvatiri kuona zvino.

0:44:12.540,0:44:19.520
Mabudiro ako; chero nguva yaunozvibata yeuka mabudiro ako.

0:44:19.520,0:44:30.240
Nguva dzose funga nezvepfungwa yako, mafungiro ako, maitiro ako achaiswa kubhengi rako.

0:44:30.240,0:44:35.040
Bhengi redu riri mune ramangwana, kwete ikozvino

0:44:35.040,0:44:38.300
Uri kurarama, uchishanda ikozvino.

0:44:38.300,0:44:44.160
Zvatiri kuita ikozvino zvichazopiwa kune remangwana redu.

0:44:44.160,0:44:46.780
Chii chauri kuita ikozvino icho chichazopihwa kune ramangwana rako?

0:44:46.780,0:44:51.540
Uri kuita zvakaipa ikozvino, uipi ihwohwo huchazopihwa kune ramangwana rako.

0:44:51.540,0:44:53.120
Uri kuita zvakanaka zvino here?

0:44:53.120,0:44:56.520
Zvakanaka zvauri kuita ikozvino zvichazopiwa kune ramangwana rako -

0:44:56.520,0:45:04.840
iwe uchazviwana munguva irikutevera, apo simba iroro renyama risisipo.

0:45:04.840,0:45:10.320
Saka ngatiyeukei ramangwana redu.

0:45:10.320,0:45:17.320
Ramangwana rangu ndiho upenyu hwangu.

0:45:17.320,0:45:21.360
Ndihwo hupenyu.

0:45:21.360,0:45:30.360
Regai nditambure iye zvino ndozofara mune ramangwana.

0:45:30.360,0:45:35.660
Asi kufara iye zvino wozotambura mune ramangwana zviri nyore

0:45:35.660,0:45:45.940
Vangani vedu; asi isu hatina kugadzirira kutambura iye zvino nekunakidzwa mune ramangwana.

0:45:45.940,0:45:55.520
Saka, zvaurikupfura ne mazviri  iwe uchimhanyira ku n'anga  uchiedza kudambura rwendo rwacho -

0:45:55.520,0:45:58.220
zviripo pakukugadzirira remangwana.

0:45:58.220,0:45:59.920
Izvi ndizvo zvandambotaura.

0:45:59.920,0:46:09.720
Mwari kazhinji anoshandisa chero chinhu chipi zvacho kuchengetedza, kugadzirira, kusimbisa chido chedu nekutsunga,

0:46:09.720,0:46:14.460
kutimisa kwekanguva ne kuronga ramangwana redu.

0:46:14.460,0:46:21.420
Svondo ye musi we Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:46:21.420,0:46:24.220
Ari kuronga ramangwana rako.

